title: Department and Title of Minister) Order 2023 (S.I. No. 19 of 2023)), with the
heading: 2. The Strategic Banking Corporation of Ireland, being a body that would,
text_raw:
2. The Strategic Banking Corporation of Ireland, being a body that would, 
but for this Order, otherwise be included in the definition of “public body” in 
subsection (1) of section 10 of the Data Sharing and Governance Act 2019 (No. 
5 of 2019), is hereby exempted. 

The Minister for Finance consents to the making of the foregoing Order. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

26 June, 2023. 

MICHAEL MCGRATH, 
Minister for Finance. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

26 June, 2023. 

PASCHAL DONOHOE, 

Minister for Public Expenditure, National Development 
Plan Delivery and Reform. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 30th June, 2023.
